Welcome on my GitHub page
=========================



Projects
--------

[JSONEventCalendar](http://dszymczuk.github.io/JSONEventCalendar/)

JSONEventCalendar is jQuery plugin to create calendar which shows events in JSON format. Each event has element like: title, date and time, type, link and more.

----------

[dsEventCalendar](http://dszymczuk.github.io/dsEventCalendar)

My first official package for Concrete 5 - Event Calendar. It is simple add on to create calendar with events and display it on page as block.


----------


[Waterfall Mixin](http://dszymczuk.github.io/waterfall-mixin/)

Small mixin for Compass to create waterfall effect for one page scroll website
